{
  "texts": [
    "The rationale was to assess whether ChatGPT can provide valid answers across various scenarios without inventing information.",
    "In all cases, the responses from ChatGPT were accurate, demonstrating the model's capability to handle direct inquiries (the functions available in simulated AV as shown in Figs.",
    "5 and 6) and hypothetical scenarios (functions not available in AV as demonstrated in Figs.",
    "7 and 8), and complex, conditional inquiries (as illustrated in the new Fig. 9) effectively.",
    "Additionally, we observed that, on average, participants asked seven questions while interacting with ChatGPT."
  ]
}